  "description": "A vibrant nighttime view of San Francisco featuring fireworks exploding above the city skyline. The Bay Bridge is prominently lit with blue and white lights, extending into the dark waters of the bay. The city's buildings are illuminated with golden and white lights, creating a sparkling contrast against the dark background. A burst of red, white, and gold fireworks illuminates the night sky above the city, adding a sense of celebration and spectacle. The water reflects the lights of the city and bridge, creating a beautiful shimmering effect. A faint orange glow on the water suggests the presence of boats or other light sources.",
